  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/308ae34a8925d31f20b50a56817c17d5.webp?t=1729140894\" width=616 height=42 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/60e9ab408d17223624206bda0e7ccccd.poster.avif?t=1729140894\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/60e9ab408d17223624206bda0e7ccccd.webm?t=1729140894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/60e9ab408d17223624206bda0e7ccccd.mp4?t=1729140894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>PLONG is a brick-breaking arcade roguelike, with each run providing a new combination of abilities and upgrades making every playthrough a unique challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/512b7cc2a2f9f340a6a08a001c955a8c.webp?t=1729140894\" width=616 height=42 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Coffee Break Arcade Roguelike!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Five Unique Abilities and over Twenty Modifiers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Procedurally Generated Stages!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam Deck compatible!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Daily Run mode!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Three more paddles than most brick breaking games!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/867d3ec34d707806851c3d956665cd06.webp?t=1729140894\" width=616 height=42 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/bbaa9d48570430854f652146eae1324f.poster.avif?t=1729140894\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/bbaa9d48570430854f652146eae1324f.webm?t=1729140894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/bbaa9d48570430854f652146eae1324f.mp4?t=1729140894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Fly through file systems, finding valuable files that will help you progress between runs and customize your PLONG application.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to become the ultimate virus and leave a trail of destruction in your wake? Travel back to 1998 and play PLONG now to find out! </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/308ae34a8925d31f20b50a56817c17d5.webp?t=1729140894\" width=616 height=42 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/60e9ab408d17223624206bda0e7ccccd.poster.avif?t=1729140894\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/60e9ab408d17223624206bda0e7ccccd.webm?t=1729140894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/60e9ab408d17223624206bda0e7ccccd.mp4?t=1729140894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>PLONG is a brick-breaking arcade roguelike, with each run providing a new combination of abilities and upgrades making every playthrough a unique challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/512b7cc2a2f9f340a6a08a001c955a8c.webp?t=1729140894\" width=616 height=42 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Coffee Break Arcade Roguelike!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Five Unique Abilities and over Twenty Modifiers!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Procedurally Generated Stages!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Steam Deck compatible!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Daily Run mode!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Three more paddles than most brick breaking games!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/867d3ec34d707806851c3d956665cd06.webp?t=1729140894\" width=616 height=42 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/bbaa9d48570430854f652146eae1324f.poster.avif?t=1729140894\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/bbaa9d48570430854f652146eae1324f.webm?t=1729140894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416290/extras/bbaa9d48570430854f652146eae1324f.mp4?t=1729140894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Fly through file systems, finding valuable files that will help you progress between runs and customize your PLONG application.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to become the ultimate virus and leave a trail of destruction in your wake? Travel back to 1998 and play PLONG now to find out! </p>",
